com.googlecode.aluminumproject.templates

Class DefaultTemplateElementFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.googlecode.aluminumproject.templates.DefaultTemplateElementFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ConfigurationElement, TemplateElementFactory

    public class DefaultTemplateElementFactory
extends Object
implements TemplateElementFactory
    A template element factory that creates default template elements.

    It's possible to configure a number of action interceptors. These will intercept all actions (as opposed to action interceptors that are supplied by action contributions, which intercept a single action only). To add action interceptors, provide a configuration parameter named "template_element_factory.default.action_interceptor.packages" or "configuration.default.configuration_element.packages" that contains one or more package names. All non-abstract action interceptors in these packages that are not annotated with @Ignored will be created and used.
